<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Dubai

United Arab Emirates
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Travel Writer, NodeJS Enthusiast and Last Second Idea Generator
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I make things look simple, cool and fun.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I do what I do because it teaches me about life, gives me sense of purpose and pushes me to learn and be more. One day, that's the reason why I'll do something else.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
I looked up in the sky and stopped for a moment. Life passes by so quickly that if we don't stop and enjoy we're going to miss the whole point of living.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
Antifragile by Nassim Taleb & Biocentrism by Robert Lanza
</p>

